102-188b @#/ /dug zhi bar byed ba zhes bya ba/ bdud rtsi sman gyi lha mo nor gyi rgyun la phyag 'tshal lo/ /tad+ya thA/ oM su ru su ru ka/ ba ra ba ra ke/ bi ri hi ri/ shud+d+he bi shud+d+he swA hA/ sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi bden pa dang gzi brjid

102-189a kyis klu'i dug dang / sbrul gyi dug dang / sbyar ba'i dug dang / kha rlangs kyi dug dang / rtsa ba'i dug dang / gcan gzan mche ba'i dug bcom mo/ /dug nges par bcom mo zhes brjod par bya'o/ /dug thams cad zhi bar byed pa'i gzungs rdzogs s+ho//
